To produce a signature for some specific file, use this command:

svn blame core/MetaBody.hpp | awk '{print $2}' | sort | uniq -c | \
sort -rn | awk '{print $2}' | \
xargs -n 1 -I person fgrep person AUTHORS | \
sed -e 's/ *[0-9]* \(.*\)/* (C) \1                 */'

